<section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Timeline marker -->
    <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8">
      <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-slate-200 flex items-center justify-center">
        <span class="font-display text-2xl text-slate-700">2000</span>
      </div>
      <div class="h-px flex-1 bg-slate-200"></div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900">
      Then the dot-com bubble burst.
    </h2>

    <div class="mt-8 space-y-6 text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        The tech economy collapsed. Colleagues lost jobs. Then they lost their houses.
      </p>

      <p>
        They'd bought at the top of their approval. No margin. No cushion. When income dropped, everything fell apart.
      </p>

      <!-- Contrast block -->
      <div class="my-10 p-8 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl">
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-700 font-medium">
          We weren't rich. But we were okay.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-slate-600">
          That wasn't luck. That was Bob.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
